{"tid":1625920,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"戰術討論「顏料」","createTime":"2019-10-05T08:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T13:14:15.000Z","uid":320131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be13980aa47abfa0356532ef083a9feb516d5ef2","tid":1625920,"uid":320131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:58:24.000Z","msg":"之前有人話用<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">顏料水</span></strong> <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>顏料水泡</strong></span>去阻擋黑警視線，但係 參考班狗既胡椒噴霧同埋水炮車之後唸到利用水壓既威力可以遠距離好似水炮車咁射班狗。<br />\n<br />\n咁即係。用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">高壓洗車槍 </span></strong>再加落平時路邊紅色既消防栓<br />\n一支唔可行既話 兩支 <br />\n分別係 一支高壓水 另一支純顏料 <br />\n射到啲狗乜都睇唔到又濕曬<br />\n討論下可以點運用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mj8a3sx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmj8a3sx.jpg&h=ec15b2de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"869df80c27406c980b1b5643d9f069bac9436347","tid":1625920,"uid":320131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e6258109283ef9b2d5b2f08178f1431bad90635","tid":1625920,"uid":320131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:48:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b3d7ddce4c66c4aae0921f71b58bd983b1e6567","tid":1625920,"uid":320131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:48:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0178ad9f637fd066f6b7252014ceef231a54cc03","tid":1625920,"uid":320131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:48:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ea94f248cfd48db63e7cc35275ef5f7a734298a","tid":1625920,"uid":320131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb1a576c0397ccc16a425719538d407f5a506ca0","tid":1625920,"uid":75264,"like":0